STATE of North Carolina
v.
Joey Parice GRAHAM No. 104P19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 9, 2019 Joey P. Graham, for Graham, Joey Parice. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, R. Andrew Murray, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 26th of March 2019 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Mecklenburg County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of May 2019."
